OL,3,CNI justice system 'crisis' as
OL,4,Cbarristers plan indefinite strike
OL,6,FCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland who are striking indefinitely
OL,8,Ffrom Monday have called for urgency in
OL,9,Faddressing the "crisis" in the justice
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,FDonal Lunny KC, chairman of the Bar
OL,13,FCouncil of Northern Ireland, said
OL,14,Fbarristers will not resume work on
OL,15,Fcrown court criminal cases.
OL,17,FHe said the Department of Justice
OL,18,Fneeded to show "pragmatism and the
OL,19,Furgency that's required to resolve the
OL,20,Fissue of crown court fees".
