OL,6,FOf the 193 members of the Criminal Bar
OL,7,FAssociation (CBA) who voted on the
OL,8,Fproposal, 89% backed a full withdrawal
OL,9,Fof services.
OL,11,FThe CBA says fees for legally aided
OL,12,Fcriminal work have not been increased
OL,13,Fsince 2005, making them worth just 50%
OL,14,Fof their original value.
OL,16,FStormont Justice Minister Naomi Long
OL,17,Fhas committed to increasing their fee
OL,18,Frates by 16%.
