OL,6,FMr Lunny said he recognised the
OL,7,Fminister was in a "difficult position"
OL,8,Fas a result of funding cuts to her
OL,9,Fdepartment, but that "in the overall
OL,10,Fscheme of the Department of Justice's
OL,11,Fbudget and funds, a relatively small
OL,12,Famount of money is all that's required
OL,13,Fto resolve this long standing problem.
