OL,6,FMr Lunny said the criminal justice
OL,7,Fsystem in Northern Ireland is headed
OL,8,Fthe same way if the problems are not
OL,9,Fresolved.
OL,11,F"In a way, the strike is a red
OL,12,Fherring. The real crisis is that
OL,13,Fbarristers and solicitors firms aren't
OL,14,Fdoing criminal work because the legal
OL,15,Faid rates are so poor," he said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@WO]
