OL,6,F"In England and Wales, even though the
OL,7,Flegal aid rates are much better than
OL,8,Fthey are here, they can't attract
OL,9,Fsufficient numbers of barristers
OL,10,Feither to do the defence work or the
OL,11,Fprosecution work, and that crisis that
OL,12,Fthey're having is where we will end up
OL,13,Fif the rates aren't improved and
OL,14,Fimproved significantly."
OL,16,FHe added that young barristers in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland "are not interested
OL,18,Fin doing crown court work because the
OL,19,Fpay is so poor, so you have an ever
OL,20,Fdwindling cohort of older barristers
OL,21,Fdoing that work".
