OL,6,FThe family of Natalie McNally, who
OL,7,Fdied after she was stabbed at her home
OL,8,Fin 2022, described the potential of
OL,9,Ffurther delays in her murder trial as
OL,10,Fa "kick in the teeth" when a judge
OL,11,Flast month cautioned the court may not
OL,12,Fbe able to proceed in January as
OL,13,Fplanned due to industrial action.
OL,15,FMr Lunny said barristers "aren't
OL,16,Fblind" to the impact the strikes will
OL,17,Fhave on victims.
OL,19,F"Barristers who are practicing in the
OL,20,Fcrown court every day know exactly how
OL,21,Ftraumatic those cases can be," he said.
OL,26,@rD@COUrD@UO]wD@ZOUxD@FO]{D@AOU}D@^O]
