OL,6,F"It won't just have an impact on
OL,7,Fvictims, it will have an impact on
OL,8,Faccused persons. It will have an
OL,9,Fimpact on witnesses. It will have an
OL,10,Fimpact on jurors, people who are asked
OL,11,Fto serve on juries, so our members are
OL,12,Fvery aware of the impact it will have.
OL,14,F"It's important to recognise that it
OL,15,Fwas very much a last resort step. It
OL,16,Fwas a step that was not lightly taken.
OL,18,F"As to how much of an impact it has,
OL,19,Fthat's very much in the hands of the
OL,20,Fdepartment.
