OL,6,F"The department, if they want to deal
OL,7,Fwith this crisis ` and there is a
OL,8,Fcrisis in the criminal justice system
OL,9,Faside from this strike ` there is a
OL,10,Fcrisis in the system that the
OL,11,Fdepartment aren't showing any urgency
OL,12,Fin attempting to tackle."
OL,14,FWhen industrial action was announced,
OL,15,FMs Long accused barristers of seeking
OL,16,Fto "leverage further trauma and stress
OL,17,Fon victims" and said she wasn't
OL,18,Fconfident "the CBA is committed to
OL,19,Fmeaningful engagement".
