OL,6,FMr Lunny said Northern Ireland's Lady
OL,7,FChief Justice Dame Siobhan Keegan
OL,8,Fadvised in November that the CBA and
OL,9,Fdepartment engage with a specialist
OL,10,Fmediator, to which the barristers
OL,11,Faccepted and the department declined.
OL,13,F"We don't know their reasons, because
OL,14,Fwe've never seen the letter that they
OL,15,Fwrote to the Lady Chief Justice, but
OL,16,Fwe have always been and we remain
OL,17,Fwilling, ready to mediate with the
OL,18,Fdepartment if they change their mind,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
