OL,6,FThe Justice minister said she is
OL,7,F"profoundly disappointed and
OL,8,Ffrustrated" by the industrial action,
OL,9,Fwhich she described as "not
OL,10,Fjustifiable or necessary".
OL,12,FMs Long said the Bar agreed to a road-
OL,13,Fmap as part of a working group chaired
OL,14,Fby His Honour Judge Tom Burgess.
OL,16,F"The road-map provided direction on
OL,17,Fall the areas the CBA has indicated
OL,18,Fmust be addressed to enable members
OL,19,Freturn to full service delivery," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@KO]qD@XOUrD@YO]xD@AOU{D@aO]
