OL,6,F"Yet, just a few days later, the CBA
OL,7,Fannounced a complete withdrawal of
OL,8,Fservices."
OL,10,FShe added: "Given Judge Burgess'
OL,11,Funique insight into the discussions
OL,12,Fwithin the working group to date, I
OL,13,Fplace significant weight on his
OL,14,Fcontinuing view that without
OL,15,Fdeveloping that evidence there can be
OL,16,Fno basis for determining what is
OL,17,Fproper and reasonable remuneration,
OL,18,Fand that any 'mediation process will
OL,19,Ffind itself in exactly the same
OL,20,Fposition as the present process'.
